293
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:54,880
Please be cautious.

294
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:58,240
Hurry up and go!

295
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,799
Stop hanging out with Wang Qinian.

296
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:01,519
I...

297
00:19:01,759 --> 00:19:02,480
What?

298
00:19:16,039 --> 00:19:17,039
Your Majesty,

299
00:19:17,039 --> 00:19:17,680
I've passed on your order

300
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:18,480
in advance.

301
00:19:19,559 --> 00:19:20,599
Those who are loyal to you

302
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,000
in different ministries

303
00:19:22,559 --> 00:19:23,319
all know that

304
00:19:23,319 --> 00:19:25,359
we'll deal with Shen Zhong today.

305
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:28,200
For those who want to help Shen Zhong
out of old friendships,

306
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:30,599
some are controlled

307
00:19:30,759 --> 00:19:31,960
