308
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,079
With my followers

309
00:19:35,599 --> 00:19:36,839
and my mother's followers

310
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,480
working together,

311
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:43,279
Shen Zhong stands no chance.

312
00:19:46,319 --> 00:19:48,039
He Daoren goes to see Fan Xian secretly.

