00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,559
Guo Baokun is the nominal Chief.

314
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:56,480
He Daoren is the actual future

315
00:19:56,519 --> 00:19:57,599
Chief of secret agents
in Shangjing Town.

316
00:19:59,000 --> 00:19:59,720
After I leave,

317
00:19:59,720 --> 00:20:01,200
you should take charge of
the intelligence network in Shangjing Town.

318
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,039
I'll try my best.

319
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,000
Take it easy.

320
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:07,400
After our smuggling business expands,

321
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:08,839
we can buy information

322
00:20:08,839 --> 00:20:10,079
openly.

323
00:20:10,559 --> 00:20:11,920
It won't be long

324
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:12,720
before secret agents
can live a safe life.

325
00:20:13,519 --> 00:20:14,279
What else do you want to tell me?

326
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:16,119
I can't stay long

327
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:18,079
for fear that I might be discovered.

328
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,359
Nothing else.

329
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,079
No need to see me before I leave.

330
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:23,559
Protect yourself. Don't be discovered.

331
00:20:33,039 --> 00:20:34,279
Your Majesty, since you've known

332
00:20:34,279 --> 00:20:35,720
He Daoren is a secret agent of Nanqing,

333
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:37,599
why not catch him?

334
00:20:38,359 --> 00:20:39,680
What can we get

335
00:20:40,079 --> 00:20:41,440
by catching him?

336
00:20:46,519 --> 00:20:47,119
Sometimes,

337
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:48,680
enemies can

338
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:49,920
do things for us.

339
00:20:51,759 --> 00:20:52,920
Look at the situation now.

340
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:55,000
Shen Zhong has no future.

341
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:57,599
Now we don't have to fight him.

342
00:20:58,880 --> 00:20:59,920
So why not use our enemies?

343
00:21:00,519 --> 00:21:01,200
But now,

344
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:02,480
He Daoren is useless

345
00:21:03,279 --> 00:21:04,599
after defeating Shen Zhong.

346
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,319
No hurry.

347
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:09,440
By keeping He Daoren,

348
00:21:10,319 --> 00:21:11,119
Nanqing can only

349
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,160
get the information

350
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:13,680
we want them to get.

351
00:21:14,839 --> 00:21:17,400
Your Majesty, you want to use He Daoren

352
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,519
to sow distrust among our enemies.

353
00:21:21,839 --> 00:21:22,960
But Her Majesty

354
00:21:23,599 --> 00:21:24,839
has got Shangshan Hu.

355
00:21:25,519 --> 00:21:27,400
Mother will never send Shangshan Hu

356
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:28,319
back to the army.

357
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:30,240
From now on,

358
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:32,720
that tiger is useless.

359
00:21:36,359 --> 00:21:37,319
I'm afraid Fan Xian

360
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:39,440
will become a formidable enemy of Beiqi.

361
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:44,319
Fan Xian will never be our enemy.

362
00:21:45,599 --> 00:21:46,400
Remember that

363
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,400
the biggest enemy

364
00:21:49,279 --> 00:21:50,599
always comes from within.

365
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:54,720
Those princes from Nanqing

366
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:59,119
are all hard to deal with.

367
00:22:00,079 --> 00:22:01,400
Fan Xian still has

368
00:22:02,599 --> 00:22:03,720
a long way to go in future.

369
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:30,079
You're leaving.

370
00:22:30,319 --> 00:22:31,839
Why ask me over?

371
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:33,839
I want to see someone.

372
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:36,119
Si Lili can't see you for sure.

373
00:22:36,839 --> 00:22:37,519
It's Zhuang Mohan.

374
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:41,200
Didn't he spit blood

375
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:42,119
after being pissed by you?

376
00:22:42,559 --> 00:22:43,279
You still can't let him go?

377
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:45,799
I was entrusted by someone
to send him a message.

378
00:22:47,759 --> 00:22:48,640
Why do you ask me for help?

379
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:50,160
You can see him yourself.

380
00:22:51,119 --> 00:22:51,880
I don't want others

381
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:52,839
to know about it.

382
00:22:55,079 --> 00:22:56,400
What about me?

383
00:22:58,279 --> 00:22:59,039
I cry, "Can't you see? Can't you see?

384
00:22:59,039 --> 00:23:00,240
The green leaves are fresh
but the red flowers are fading!"

385
00:23:00,319 --> 00:23:01,319
You're crabapple blossoms.

386
00:23:01,319 --> 00:23:01,920
You're no mortal.

387
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:05,000
You're smooth-tongued

388
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:06,160
when asking for help.

389
00:23:08,319 --> 00:23:08,920
Do me a favor.

390
00:23:11,640 --> 00:23:12,559
I assure you

391
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:13,839
it won't harm Beiqi.

392
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:15,160
Nor will I scold him.

393
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:55,799
Master Zhuang.

394
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:04,400
No need to stand up.

395
00:24:05,759 --> 00:24:06,200
Fine.

396
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:07,319
Take a seat! Take a seat! Take a seat!

397
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:13,440
Look!

398
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:17,759
The line "One who has seen the ocean
thinks nothing of mere rivers.

399
00:24:17,839 --> 00:24:19,839
One who has appreciated the clouds over
the Wushan Mountain sees nothing of mere clouds."

400
00:24:21,319 --> 00:24:23,839
has beautiful diction
and neat antithesis.

401
00:24:24,480 --> 00:24:25,880
But without knowing the context of
the latter sentence,

402
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:28,759
it doesn't

403
00:24:29,319 --> 00:24:30,000
make any sense.

404
00:24:30,799 --> 00:24:32,200
It really doesn't make any sense.

405
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:35,519
Wushan Mountain
is a holy mountain in the far south.

406
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:38,000
This mountain is renowned for
its unparalleled cloudscape.

407
00:24:38,559 --> 00:24:39,880
The latter sentence uses its name

408
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:41,599
to express the loyalty in love.

409
00:24:42,039 --> 00:24:43,160
I see.

410
00:24:43,799 --> 00:24:44,480
I've checked

411
00:24:45,960 --> 00:24:47,200
many books,

412
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:50,319
but I just couldn't find
Wushan Mountain.

413
00:24:52,079 --> 00:24:53,480
Luckily, you explained it to me.

414
00:24:55,319 --> 00:24:56,680
Are you annotating
the poetry collection?

415
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:57,480
Yes.

416
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,200
I have another question.

417
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:01,720
Look!

418
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:04,640
Prince Chen paid at a banquet
in the Palace of Perfection.

419
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:07,759
Ten thousand coins for a cask of wine,
with many a laugh and quip.

420
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:09,519
What's the literary quotation?

421
00:25:10,839 --> 00:25:11,799
Prince Chen

422
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:13,599
is a prince surnamed Cao.

423
00:25:14,079 --> 00:25:15,240
He once held a banquet

424
00:25:15,319 --> 00:25:16,039
in the Palace of Perfection.

425
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:18,000
A prince surnamed Cao?

426
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:20,160
In past dynasties,

427
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:22,440
no one from the imperial families
was surnamed Cao.

428
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,200
Master Zhuang,

429
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:27,319
I told you

430
00:25:27,799 --> 00:25:28,599
on the Hall of Prayer for Good Harvest

431
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,359
that all these poems come from

432
00:25:30,359 --> 00:25:31,559
another world.

433
00:25:31,839 --> 00:25:32,960
So these literary quotations certainly

434
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,519
won't be found in historical records.

435
00:25:38,319 --> 00:25:38,880
Then,

436
00:25:40,680 --> 00:25:42,839
it's a fairyland in dream?

437
00:25:43,119 --> 00:25:44,680
It's not a fairyland. It's...

438
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:45,400
What?

439
00:25:45,640 --> 00:25:46,799
It's the imprint left by

440
00:25:46,799 --> 00:25:47,559
another era.

441
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:48,319
What?

442
00:25:49,759 --> 00:25:50,640
Era?

443
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:53,680
It is earlier than all history

444
00:25:54,599 --> 00:25:55,839
for hundreds and thousands of years.

445
00:25:58,240 --> 00:25:59,200
It's a splendid

446
00:25:59,200 --> 00:26:00,200
civilization

447
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:01,680
lost in the

448
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:02,839
river of time.

449
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:09,480
I don't get it. I don't get it.

450
00:26:10,160 --> 00:26:10,720
Are you referring to

451
00:26:11,119 --> 00:26:12,400
the ancient times?

452
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:13,839
It's even earlier than that.

453
00:26:14,319 --> 00:26:15,839
How do you know these?

454
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,759
Since I was born,

455
00:26:19,279 --> 00:26:19,799
these things

456
00:26:19,799 --> 00:26:21,000
have been carved in my mind

457
00:26:22,039 --> 00:26:23,480
as if I've seen them in my dreams.

458
00:26:27,079 --> 00:26:29,039
So it is

459
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:31,200
a dreamland.

460
00:26:31,759 --> 00:26:32,680
Can I put it this way?

461
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:34,400
Yes, you can.

462
00:26:39,119 --> 00:26:39,680
Good.

463
00:26:41,079 --> 00:26:43,960
Now I understand why there're so many

464
00:26:43,960 --> 00:26:45,359
unknown literary quotations.

465
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:49,640
It's not because I'm a poor scholar.

466
00:26:50,599 --> 00:26:52,880
How can I know stuff

467
00:26:54,720 --> 00:26:55,720
of the fairyland?

468
00:26:58,880 --> 00:27:00,200
Don't let it bother you.

469
00:27:03,839 --> 00:27:04,359
Fine.

470
00:27:15,720 --> 00:27:16,720
When you came in just now,

471
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:19,039
why was there no report?

472
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:21,160
Actually,

473
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:22,440
I sneaked in to see you.

474
00:27:22,839 --> 00:27:23,680
Your servant was lured away

475
00:27:23,799 --> 00:27:24,839
by my friend.

476
00:27:28,119 --> 00:27:29,799
Why do you sneak in?

477
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:32,119
Actually, I know

478
00:27:32,119 --> 00:27:33,519
you are in Shangjing,

479
00:27:34,079 --> 00:27:35,599
and I want to see you very much.

480
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:37,880
But my servant stops me

481
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:38,720
from visiting you.

482
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:41,160
He said my condition would go worse

483
00:27:42,599 --> 00:27:44,319
if I see you.

484
00:27:46,759 --> 00:27:47,680
Master Zhuang, are you sick?

485
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,880
I'm just old.

486
00:28:05,359 --> 00:28:06,359
Don't! Don't! Don't!

487
00:28:16,559 --> 00:28:17,200
Your Excellency,

488
00:28:18,599 --> 00:28:19,680
back on the Hall of Prayer
for Good Harvest,

489
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:22,799
I framed you up.

490
00:28:24,599 --> 00:28:25,599
Till today,

491
00:28:25,799 --> 00:28:27,240
I feel guilty all the time.

492
00:28:28,319 --> 00:28:28,920
Today,

493
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:31,079
by seeing you,

494
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:34,519
I can finally apologize to you
in person.

495
00:28:35,599 --> 00:28:36,559
Your Excellency,

496
00:28:38,119 --> 00:28:39,880
please be magnanimous and forgive me.

497
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,680
Master Zhuang, you don't have to!

498
00:28:47,599 --> 00:28:48,799
I know you did that

499
00:28:49,359 --> 00:28:50,599
to save Xiao En.

500
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:55,400
To be honest,

501
00:28:57,039 --> 00:28:58,160
though he is surnamed Xiao,

502
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:01,839
he's my full brother.

503
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:06,240
Actually, Master Zhuang,
I visit you this time

504
00:29:07,839 --> 00:29:09,359
because Senior Xiao asked me to.

505
00:29:14,839 --> 00:29:15,480
Really?

506
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:20,039
He finally wants

507
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:22,119
to contact me.

508
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:24,880
Did he ask you

509
00:29:26,759 --> 00:29:28,039
to tell me anything?

510
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:36,359
What's wrong?

511
00:29:39,720 --> 00:29:40,680
Is he dead?

512
00:29:57,279 --> 00:29:57,960
All men

513
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:00,880
must die.

514
00:30:03,119 --> 00:30:05,200
Senior Xiao died in peace.

515
00:30:08,200 --> 00:30:10,400
He lived a miserable life.

516
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:13,519
That's because

517
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:17,440
he killed so many people.

518
00:30:19,759 --> 00:30:20,559
Nowadays, man gets power

519
00:30:21,200 --> 00:30:22,960
by killing others
and setting places on fire.

520
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:25,039
Your Excellency Fan,

521
00:30:26,359 --> 00:30:27,799
you shouldn't be like that.

522
00:30:29,279 --> 00:30:31,000
Man like you
who's capable of writing wonderful poems

523
00:30:32,599 --> 00:30:34,759
shouldn't be defiled by
the secular world.

524
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:36,759
Master Zhuang, I promise you.

525
00:30:38,799 --> 00:30:39,799
I'll never be like that.

526
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,079
Good!

527
00:30:56,839 --> 00:30:58,359
Isn't that Commander Shen?

528
00:30:59,519 --> 00:31:00,440
Her Majesty ordered you

529
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,519
to rest at home for a few days.

530
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:05,559
But our Division can't operate

531
00:31:06,079 --> 00:31:07,640
without a leader.

532
00:31:08,400 --> 00:31:08,960
There's no other way.

533
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:10,720
From tomorrow on,

534
00:31:11,039 --> 00:31:13,319
I'll take your position temporarily.

535
00:31:14,039 --> 00:31:16,200
Feel relieved to rest at home.

536
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:17,799
Just leave

537
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:18,839
all the trouble

538
00:31:19,279 --> 00:31:20,279
to me.

539
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:33,720
Your Excellency,

540
00:31:35,079 --> 00:31:36,400
why are you still here?

541
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,160
Seriously speaking,

542
00:31:38,480 --> 00:31:39,880
you're defying the imperial order.

543
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:41,480
Don't make it hard for me.

544
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:44,839
Should I find someone to help you?

545
00:31:54,440 --> 00:31:54,920
Who are you?

546
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:56,440
How dare you break into the Division?

547
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,839
What we're going to do today is simple.

548
00:32:16,720 --> 00:32:18,240
Stop and kill the Nanqing mission.

549
00:32:19,759 --> 00:32:20,519
There's no imperial edict.

550
00:32:21,799 --> 00:32:23,200
It's my own decision.

551
00:32:25,799 --> 00:32:26,359
Everyone,

552
00:32:27,599 --> 00:32:30,039
succeed or not,

553
00:32:31,119 --> 00:32:32,720
this operation will cost your lives.

554
00:32:35,039 --> 00:32:36,279
I'm also afraid to die.

555
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,079
But on second thought,

556
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:42,359
if I can save Beiqi

557
00:32:44,960 --> 00:32:47,160
by sacrificing my life,

558
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:51,240
it's totally worth it.

559
00:32:54,079 --> 00:32:56,359
With me or not, it's up to you.

560
00:32:57,039 --> 00:32:57,839
I won't force you.

561
00:33:00,799 --> 00:33:01,480
Commander Shen,

562
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:03,759
you should think is through.

563
00:33:04,799 --> 00:33:05,240
Guards!

564
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,039
You traitors,

565
00:33:18,359 --> 00:33:19,200
how dare you

566
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:20,119
do this?

567
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:21,359
Whoever leaves

568
00:33:21,839 --> 00:33:22,559
will be killed!

569
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:26,680
Do you know

570
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,240
